component.illusobjdesc:
Five birds soar on extended wings: two fly above line two of the plate: "A Memorable Fancy"; 
                     one flies over the word "perswaded" in line 11; and a particularly small bird appears above "perception" 
                     in line 9.  The largest of the birds has a wingspread the length of the word "cause" in line 7, over which it flies.
